# Next.js (App Router)

- Default to Server Components; add `"use client"` only when needed (state, effects, browser APIs).
- Call the API from Server Components or Route Handlers — never expose internal endpoints to the browser.
- Keep `page.tsx` files thin; extract logic into components and utilities.
